GoPhish is a web-based framework to make setting up phishing campaigns
more straightforward. GoPhish allows you to store your SMTP server settings
for sending emails, has a web-based tool for creating email templates using 
a simple WYSIWYG (What You See Is What You Get) editor. You can also schedule
when emails are sent and have an analytics dashboard that shows how many emails
have been sent, opened or clicked.
Source: https://getgophish.com/
